Class Path

java.lang.Object
Path
Direct Known Subclasses:
CareerPath, ChangeCareerPath, CollegePath, StartFamilyPath
public abstract class Path
extends java.lang.Object
This class defines the structure blocks of the game, the paths. Paths are made up of spaces.

  • Field Summary

    Fields 
    Modifier and Type Field Description
    protected Space destinationSpace
    This attribute stores the last space of the path.
    protected Space originSpace
    This attribute stores the first space of the path.
    protected java.util.ArrayList<Space> spaces
    This attribute holds all of the spaces that belong to this path.
